{"tid":1458723,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日係外國飛返嚟 但架機被cancel","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:41.000Z","uid":109889,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1274c70a462273b64c670f1e15d981da677d16ae","tid":1458723,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"今日係外國飛香港 唔係直機<br />\n但係到咗機場個counter話因為香港依加既情況<br />\n佢地既公司唔敢亦都冇指示會係未來兩日有飛機去香港<br />\n跟住佢地就慰問香港既情況 話佢地都明白香港既難處<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢一刻好無助 但想講你地去機場真係有用<br />\nBook多幾晚酒店 打多幾次電話去吹佢地對我嚟講唔係難事<br />\n所以你地一定要堅持自己既目的<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 心情有啲激動<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警察還眼</span></strong>"},{"pid":"743c90da53dd90b83f31a0e99f2c09b0eeccef33","tid":1458723,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"d6d48a75e1d203fddbcdc41306ba2538db051cc4","tid":1458723,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21e7a4a6285a503475bdfc21a84af9b44d52078b","tid":1458723,"uid":212973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"多謝支持"}]}